        @if (ViewBag.Checkbox58 != String.Empty)
        {
            <p> B. <i>SUPPLIER</i> certifies it has paid, offered to pay, or agreed to pay any "fees", "commissions", or "political contributions" as defined in 22 CFR &sect; 130.5 and 22 CFR &sect; 130.6 in connection with the sale of defense articles, technical data, and/or defense services to Honeywell.</p>

        
            <p style="margin-left:20px">
                <b style="margin-left:40px"><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox59 /> YES </b>
                <b style="margin-left:20px"><input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox60 /> NO </b>
            </p>
        }
        <p>
            NOTE:  22 CFR &sect; 130.9(d) requires <i>SUPPLIER</i> to inform Honeywell as soon as possible if <i>SUPPLIER</i> subsequently learns that it paid, offered to pay, or agreed to pay any fees, commissions, or political contributions in connection with the sale of defense articles, technical data, and/or defense services to Honeywell.         
        </p>
        <p><b><i style="color:red;"><u>If Item B. is YES, please complete Exhibit I</u> for each fee, commission, and political contribution, using additional sheets as necessary, referencing the Sales Order/Contract Number at issue, and numbering each successive sheet X of X accordingly.</i></b></p>

